    BiocGenerics,
    Biostrings,
    GenomicAlignments,
    GenomicFeatures,
    GenomeInfoDb,
    igraph,
    parallel,
    Rsamtools,
    rtracklayer,
    RUnit,
    S4Vectors
Suggests:
