    BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.knownGene
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: AlternativeSplicing, RNASeq, Transcription
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
